  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this Style starting at 3rd level, you have trained your legs until you feel the urge to run at all times. Your base movement speed increases by +10 feet, on top of your speed increases from the <em><strong>Enhanced Movement</strong></em> table. This increase in movement speed increases as you gain levels in this class, as indicated by the <em><strong>Turbulence Speed Chart</strong></em>.</p><p>Your unarmed attacks must use your legs to use any of this subclass' active features.</p><img src=\"systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Cheat%20Sheet/T7%20Turbulence%20Speed%20Chart.png\" />",
